data.content:
Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘['trʌstiη]
 Cách viết khác:
 trustful
◘['trʌstfl]
 ■như trustful

Anh - Anh
trusting
■ adjective showing trust in or tending to trust others; not suspicious.
Derivatives
trustinglyadverb
trustingnessnoun

Từ điển Đồng nghĩa
trusting
▸ adjective TRUSTFUL, unsuspecting, unquestioning, unguarded, unwary; naive, innocent, childlike, ingenuous, wide-eyed, credulous, gullible, easily taken in.
Opposites
distrustful, suspicious.
